snippet.title: ABC News (Australia)
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official ABC News channel. As well as our 24-hour live stream, we also livestream breaking news events (make sure you subscribe and tap the bell so you don't miss any important notifications) and The Drum each weekday evening.

This channel also features regular news updates from the Australian Broadcasting Corporation. Our programs include 7.30, The Business, The Drum, Insiders and The World.

If you're looking for our long-form programs Foreign Correspondent, Four Corners and Australian Story, head over to the ABC News In-depth channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/ABCNewsIndepth
